<dl id="n05110g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n05" href="#n05110g">N05 (VI.B.2)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n05all.htm#n05110g"> 110(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Dream of Gerontius </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: The Dream of Gerontius is a poem by John Henry Cardinal Newman. It relates the journey of a pious man&apos;s soul from his deathbed to his judgment before God and settling into Purgatory. It was set to music in 1900 by Edward Elgar, for voices and orchestra in two parts, Op. 38. <font color="green">[Henkes]</font> </mm> </dd></dl>
